UwbRtls
=======

This library contains, under src/dw1000/, an unmodified copy of the low-level
register driver from the arduino-dw1000 project:

    arduino-dw1000
    Copyright (c) 2015 by Thomas Trojer <thomas@trojer.net>
    https://github.com/thotro/arduino-dw1000
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0 (see src/dw1000/LICENSE.md).

Only the low-level transceiver driver is vendored:
    DW1000.{h,cpp}, DW1000Time.{h,cpp}, DW1000Constants.h,
    DW1000CompileOptions.h, deprecated.h, require_cpp11.h

The high-level protocol layer of that project (DW1000Ranging / DW1000Device /
DW1000Mac) is deliberately NOT included. Its auto-discovery ranging state
machine is the source of the ~4-anchor and single-tag limitations this library
exists to remove; the protocol/scheduling layer here (TwrEngine, UwbScheduler,
HostLink) is an original reimplementation.

The asymmetric double-sided two-way-ranging estimator used in TwrEngine follows
the well-known Decawave formulation (also used by the upstream project).
